## Limitations
The primary limitation of this report is the generalization of Native American views, as there were hundreds of tribes with diverse cultures and beliefs. Additionally, much of the historical information is derived from European accounts, which may not fully or accurately represent Native American perspectives. Further research into specific tribal histories and oral traditions would provide a more nuanced understanding of the topic.